                        </extent>
                        <foliation>
                           <p>European numerals in pencil.</p>
                        </foliation>
                        <condition>
                           <p>Folios are in relatively good condition in comparison with the folios of MS RSPA 85, its sister manuscript and the first half of the same text. There is some worm damage across the MS and between ff. 100 and 103 there is a large ink stain which permeates through the folios.</p>
                        </condition>
                     </supportDesc>
                     <layoutDesc>
                        <layout columns="1" writtenLines="24">
                           <p>Uniform layout of one column of 24 lines per page written in the coloured text box.</p>
                        </layout>
                     </layoutDesc>
