                  <additions>
                     <p>As in MS RSPA 85, there are copious marginal annotations by an array of different hands, including on f1r before the text begins.</p>
                     <p>On f1v, William Jones has written "The Hiāyah, W. Jones".</p>
                  </additions>
                  <bindingDesc>
                     <p>Red European style Indian binding with circular patterned stamped border.</p>
                  </bindingDesc>
