                  <provenance>
                     <p>RSPA 1-118 were presented to the Royal Society in January 1792 by Sir William and Lady Jones. According to the Wilkins Catalogue, this MS was presented to the Royal Society by Lady Jones.</p>
                     <p>The Royal Society's collection of 280 Persian and Arabic, and 86 Sanskrit manuscripts were transferred to the India Office Library in 1876.</p>
